Mediations:

"Since 2004 [http://www.exit-online.org/ Exit!] has published eleven issues, most recently in July 2013. Krisis 33, the journal’s last paper issue, was published in 2010; the journal recently switched to an online-only format whereby theoretical articles of often substantial length are published on the organization’s [http://www.krisis.org/ website]; as Beiträge or contributions (in line with the journal’s subtitle of '''“Contributions to the Critique of Commodity Society”)''' alongside more journalistic and blog-style pieces. Both organizations also organize a weekend-long public seminar involving (usually) four presentations by regular contributors and occasionally invited guests, and lengthy discussion."

(https://www.mediationsjournal.org/articles/editors-note-vol-27-no-1)


